    "Using this definition of user activity, we can visualize the total amount of active users as well as turnover rates (switch from active to inactive and vice versa) over time (Fig. 2).",
    "In the beginning of 2020, we have around 2800 active users per week.",
    "This number gradually decreases to roughly 1,800 until we approach the outbreak of the war.",
    "Afterwards, the number of active users starts increasing again.",
    "Note the drop and subsequent spike in activity shortly before and with the outbreak of the war."
